OL,3,CElliot Anderson calls Man City the
OL,4,C'kings of Manchester' after signing
OL,6,FElliot Anderson has declared
OL,7,FManchester City the "kings of
OL,8,FManchester" after completing a #116
OL,9,Fmillion move from Nottingham Forest.
OL,11,FThe England midfielder's five-year
OL,12,Fcontract was agreed earlier in July
OL,13,Fbut finalised following his return
OL,14,Ffrom the World Cup.
OL,16,FAnderson, 23, said he was "over the
OL,17,Fmoon" to be signing for "one of the
OL,18,Fbiggest clubs in the world" and has
OL,19,Fhis sights firmly set on winning
OL,20,Ftrophies.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
