CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784881094
OL,3,CElliot Anderson calls Man City the
OL,4,C'kings of Manchester' after signing
OL,6,FHe said: "I can't wait to play for
OL,7,Fthis club, it's a club built to win
OL,8,Ftrophies and compete at the very top
OL,9,Fof the game. That is exciting for any
OL,10,Ffootballer.
OL,12,F"I think they're winners, they're
OL,13,Frelentless, and that's the sort of
OL,14,Fteam I want to be a part of. Over the
OL,15,Flast 10, 12 years, they've dominated,
OL,16,Fso that's why I wanted to join."
OL,18,FCity are due to face Manchester United
OL,19,Fat Old Trafford on 13 September, with
OL,20,FAnderson calling it "one of the
OL,21,Fbiggest derbies in the world".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
