PN,36603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784881094
OL,3,CElliot Anderson calls Man City the
OL,4,C'kings of Manchester' after signing
OL,6,FHe said: "For as long as I've known
OL,7,FManchester, City have been the kings
OL,8,Fof Manchester. It'll be a great
OL,9,Ffixture and I can't wait to be
OL,10,Finvolved in something like that."
OL,12,FAnderson started his career in the
OL,13,Fyouth ranks at Newcastle - making 55
OL,14,Ffirst-team appearances for the club -
OL,15,Fbefore earning the nickname 'Geordie
OL,16,FMaradona' while on loan at Bristol
OL,17,FRovers.
OL,19,FHe joined Nottingham Forest in 2024 in
OL,20,F#35 million deal, playing 92 times for
OL,21,Fthe reds.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
