OL,3,CElliot Anderson calls Man City the
OL,4,C'kings of Manchester' after signing
OL,6,FAnderson was also a key member of
OL,7,FThomas Tuchel's squad in his first
OL,8,FEngland call-up at the 2026 World Cup.
OL,10,FHe said: "I'm only 23, so I've got
OL,11,Fplenty of time to get to my best
OL,12,Flevels," he said. "I'm definitely not
OL,13,Fthere yet and there's more to come
OL,14,Ffrom me.
OL,16,F"I think I bring a bit of everything.
OL,17,FI bring quality, I bring physicality,
OL,18,Fenergy. I'd like to think I'd get the
OL,19,Ffans excited, get them off their feet
OL,20,Fand bring energy to the team."
OL,26,@tD@HO]tD@SOU
