OL,3,CElliot Anderson calls Man City the
OL,4,C'kings of Manchester' after signing
OL,6,FThe midfielder said this move is
OL,7,Fparticularly special as he grew up
OL,8,Fidolising former City star Kevin De
OL,9,FBruyne.
OL,11,FHe said: "I think Kevin De Bruyne is
OL,12,Fsomeone who I've hugely looked up to
OL,13,Fover the past seven or eight years.
OL,15,F"I've always wanted to play like him.
OL,16,FI've watched him all the time and to
OL,17,Fbe sat here in the team that he was
OL,18,Fdoing it for is so special."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
