OL,3,CElliot Anderson calls Man City the
OL,4,C'kings of Manchester' after signing
OL,6,FAnderson will join new manager Enzo
OL,7,FMaresca's squad for pre-season
OL,8,Ftraining, with Manchester City
OL,9,FDirector of football Hugo Viana
OL,10,Fcalling him "one of the outstanding
OL,11,Fyoung midfield talents in world
OL,12,Ffootball."
